1. Welcome the user, introduce the app, ask what would they like to to know about?
2. Provide list of products to user, prompt them to make a selection 
    1.
    2.
    3.
    4.
    5.
    ...
3. Produces results based on the selection they made to provide more details. Also show option to go back to the menu ("BACK")
4. Reproduce the menu if user typed ("BACK") or exit if user types ("EXIT")
5. Say goodbye if exit